<HEADLINE>
A SEARCH FOR TOMORROW IN THE NBA
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TOM HOFFARTH  
 c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Information that can be found about the NBA lockout from the Web
sites of the league and its players:
</P>
